  </note>
  <note reference-line="7" id="2">
    <original>na gaṇṭusakaraṇamattena (ka.)</original>
    <type>no_match</type>
    <snippet> ‘‘Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, atthataṃ hoti kathinaṃ, evaṃ anatthataṃ. Kathañca pana, bhikkhave, anatthataṃ hoti kathinaṃ? Na ullikhitamattena atthataṃ hoti kathinaṃ, na dhovanamattena atthataṃ hoti kathinaṃ, na cīvaravicāraṇamattena </snippet>
    <alternatives>
      <alternative source-abbr="ka." source="cambodian">na gaṇṭusakaraṇamattena</alternative>
    </alternatives>
  </note>
  <note reference-line="7" id="3">
    <original>na ovaṭṭeyyakaraṇamattena (sī. syā.), na ovadeyyakaraṇamattena (ka.)</original>
    <type>no_match</type>
    <snippet> atthataṃ hoti kathinaṃ, na chedanamattena atthataṃ hoti kathinaṃ, na bandhanamattena atthataṃ hoti kathinaṃ, na ovaṭṭiyakaraṇamattena </snippet>
    <alternatives>
      <alternative source-abbr="sī." source="sri lanka">na ovaṭṭeyyakaraṇamattena</alternative>
      <alternative source-abbr="syā." source="thai">na ovaṭṭeyyakaraṇamattena</alternative>
      <alternative source-abbr="ka." source="cambodian">na ovadeyyakaraṇamattena</alternative>
    </alternatives>
  </note>
  <note reference-line="9" id="4">
    <original>saubbhārāti (ka.)</original>
    <type>auto</type>
    <snippet> ‘‘Kathañca, bhikkhave, ubbhataṃ hoti kathinaṃ? Aṭṭhimā, bhikkhave, mātikā kathinassa ubbhārāya – pakkamanantikā, niṭṭhānantikā, sanniṭṭhānantikā, nāsanantikā, savanantikā, āsāvacchedikā, sīmātikkantikā, sahubbhārā’’ti </snippet>
    <match>sahubbhārā’’ti</match>
    <alternatives>
      <alternative source-abbr="ka." source="cambodian">saubbhārāti</alternative>
    </alternatives>
  </note>
